c function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/4514/', '', 'Salicylic acid, Choline salicylate, Ziconotide, Diflunisal, Methoxyflurane, Salsalate, Acetylsalicylic acid, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone, Naltrexone', 'Oliceridine, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Acetaminophen, Dezocine, Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, Pentazocine, Dihydrocodeine, Codeine, Diamorphine, More', 1767369485);
