moglobin-inducing agents.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/4530/', '', 'Salicylic acid, Choline salicylate, Ziconotide, Diflunisal, Methoxyflurane, Salsalate, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naltrexone, Oxymorphone, Oxycodone, Methadone, More', '', 1767369485);
